content:
DO THE MATH!
#vaccinesharm #chemicalpoisoning
EPA “safe” daily level of Hg 0.1 mcg per kg.
A 2 month old infant at 5 kg x 0.1 mcg = 0.5 mcg of Hg “safe” limit.
By 2 month a baby may receive up to 62.5 mcg of Hg via routine vaccination.
